{"id":232929961,"title":"其實你可以不用拿發票","content":"每天錢包裡面一大堆的發票，塞得滿滿的比錢還要多\n其實他的存在，除了對獎好像有沒有什麼用處，說穿了其實就是\n「浪費」\n之後每次整理還要丟掉\n\n但其實你可以不用這麼浪費，現在有了解決得方法，就是你的手機，只要上網登錄你的手機號碼，再下載app，就可以在結帳的時候把手機拿給店員掃條碼，手機就會幫你記錄你的發票囉！（想看的時候直接拿手機出來看就可以了呢！）\n\n如果中獎了，也會直接給你通知～很方便吧！\n首先先上網登錄\nhttps://www.einvoice.nat.gov.tw/APCONSUMER/BTC501W/\nhttps://i.imgur.com/1UN44BO.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/aNWd0Bz.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/arzBp9n.jpg\n\nhttps://www.einvoice.nat.gov.tw/APCONSUMER/BTC501W/\n然後要記得下載app，app會顯示你的專屬條碼喔！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/W3fLlsL.jpg\n蘋果：\nhttps://apps.apple.com/us/app/%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%80%E7%99%BC%E7%A5%A8%E5%85%8C%E7%8D%8E/id1445981329?l=zh&ls=1\n\n安卓：\nhttps://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tw.gov.invoice\n\n過新年的時候，趕快把一家老小的手機都安裝好，大家一起對發票，恭喜發財！","excerpt":"每天錢包裡面一大堆的發票，塞得滿滿的比錢還要多，其實他的存在，除了對獎好像有沒有什麼用處，說穿了其實就是，「浪費」之後每次整理還要丟掉，但其實你可以不用這麼浪費，現在有了解決得方法，就是你的手機，只要","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-21T04:21:23.309Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-21T04:21:23.309Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":36,"tags":[],"topics":["環保","愛地球"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立屏東大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":36}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/1UN44BO.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/aNWd0Bz.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/arzBp9n.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/W3fLlsL.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"7836877c-f2db-4fb2-8379-aca5a43a051a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/1UN44BOl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/1UN44BOl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/1UN44BOl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTAT